Deployment updates and Rollback:
================================

    - New Deployment creates a new Rollout
    - New Rollout creates a new Revision


    Deployment Stratesgies:
    =======================

    - Recreate - All Down and All Up
    - Rolling Update - one by one Down and up


    kubectl apply -f deploy-def.yml
    


    kubectl create -f deploy-def.yml --record
    kubectl rollout status deployment/myapp-deployment
    kubectl rollout history deployment/myapp-deployment
    kubectl delete deployment myapp-deployment
    kubectl get all
    kubectl apply -f deploy-def.yml
    kubectl get deployment
    kubectl get pods
    kubectl describe deployment
    kubectl rollout undo deployment/myapp-deployment

